metadata.author: Yoto
metadata.description:
Dino Rock is a high-energy collection of songs that fuses the power of classic rock with the roar of the dinosaurs. 

Designed for kids but crafted with musical depth, each track tells the story of a different dinosaur—from the mighty T-Rex to the misunderstood Spinosaurus—with all the swagger of ‘80s metal and a sense of humor that parents will appreciate as much as their kids do. 

Every song is packed with character-driven lyrics, guitar-powered hooks, and beats that invite headbanging, dancing, and even the occasional air guitar solo. Whether your child loves stomping through the house as a Velociraptor or singing along with the gentle Brontosaurus anthem, Dino Rock brings prehistoric creatures to life in a way that feels both cool and age-appropriate. 

Dino Rock is more than just music—it’s a full-on rock adventure. It celebrates bravery, friendship, and identity through the lens of ancient giants, helping kids explore big feelings with a smile. Rock-loving parents, if you’ve been waiting for something your kids love that you won’t get tired of—this is it.

Discover: 1 track. 
Available until 30th June. 
Full Card: 8 tracks. 
For ages 3-14
